00:00:45.320 --> 00:00:46.320
lives.

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:50.429
A gamer his whole life, Steve has been focused
on strength training and exercise as a hobby

00:00:50.429 --> 00:00:56.039
for the past ten years, as an obsession, as
an obsession for the past five years, and

00:00:56.039 --> 00:01:02.230
as a full-time job for the past year. Currently
on his epic quest of awesomeness, a 35000

00:01:02.230 --> 00:01:06.290
mile trip around the world, Steve has exercised
everywhere and anywhere getting in the best

00:01:06.290 --> 00:01:11.290
shape of his life despite living out of a
backpack and never setting foot in a gym.

00:01:11.290 --> 00:01:15.690
In between workouts, he's rock climbed in
Thailand, scuba dived the Great Barrier Reef

00:01:15.690 --> 00:01:21.360
in Australia, sky dived in New Zealand, and
